  m_Maskable: 1
  m_OnCullStateChanged:
    m_PersistentCalls:
      m_Calls: []
  m_text: '<indent=-40>/hide :</indent> Toggle GM hide

    <indent=-40>/speed #
    :</indent> Changes move speed to #ms per tile.

    <indent=-40>/admin :</indent>
    Enables both /hide and sets /speed to 50.

    <indent=-40>/summon {monster}
    {number} :</indent> Summon a monster by name. Number is optional.

    <indent=-40>/warp
    {mapName} {x} {y} :</indent> Warp to a map by name. X and Y values are optional,
    if omitted you''ll appear at a random location.

    <indent=-40>/kill :</indent>
    Kills all monsters currently on screen. They will not reward experience.

    <indent=-40>/killall
    :</indent> Same as /kill, but kills all monsters on the map.

    <indent=-40>/reloadscript
    :</indent> Reloads all script and database files on the server. This is an intensive
    process and can crash the server if there are any errors with any scripts, so
    be careful!'
